snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: POPGOES Arcade (Official)
snippet.description:
A new Five Nights at Freddy's game has released!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1986840/POPGOES_Arcade/

POPGOES Arcade is an official FNAF RPG spinoff where you play as Popgoes the Weasel and save the world from bad guys like Bonnie, Chica, Foxy, and more! This is part of "POPGOES", a Five Nights at Freddy's series produced and licensed by Scott Cawthon but developed by fans as part of the "Fazbear Fanverse Initiative".

Five Nights at Freddy's by Scott Cawthon
POPGOES by Kane Carter
